msgid "Module for managing cadence workflows and runtime activity sequences."
msgstr "Module de gestion des flux de travail de cadence et des sequences d'activites."

msgid ""
"Migrated signal and timezone imports to the horilla shims, standardized "
"first-party import groups, and added class and method docstrings for pylint "
"compliance."
msgstr ""
"Migration des imports de signaux et de fuseaux horaires vers les shims "
"horilla, standardisation des groupes d'imports et ajout de docstrings pour "
"la conformite pylint."

msgid ""
"Cadence forms aligned with HorillaModelForm layout: field_order, Meta.fields "
"= \"__all__\", Meta.exclude, and keep_on_form; save logic and HTMX unchanged."
msgstr ""
"Les formulaires de cadence ont ete alignes sur le layout HorillaModelForm : "
"field_order, Meta.fields, Meta.exclude et keep_on_form ; logique de "
"sauvegarde et HTMX inchanges."

msgid ""
"Release 1.10: cadences ship under contrib with app label cadences. Signals, "
"registrations, URLs, and static paths updated to match the new contrib "
"layout."
msgstr ""
"Version 1.10 : les cadences sont integrees sous contrib avec le label "
"d'application cadences. Signaux, enregistrements, URLs et chemins statiques "
"mis a jour."

msgid ""
"Implemented cadence signals for runtime activities, enabling automated "
"cadence-driven workflow execution and activity tracking."
msgstr ""
"Implementation des signaux de cadence pour les activites d'execution, "
"permettant l'execution automatisee des flux de travail pilotes par cadence "
"et le suivi des activites."

